						"copy": "Cloudflare's customers include many large content creators, and we take the challenge of protecting their copyrighted content seriously. Cloudflare's services help our customers protect their intellectual property against malicious bots and crawlers attempting to scrape or alter the content of their sites, and we can improve the user experience by speeding up websites.  We work with rightsholders around the world to identify the ways that we believe we can best assist copyright holders concerned about infringing content on the Internet.\n",
