													"value": "Although less common, we also take other steps to address copyright complaints consistent with the frameworks established under United States law (the Digital Millennium Copyright Act) and European law (the e-Commerce Directive). In the rare instance that we receive a copyright complaint regarding content that we host, we will remove or disable access to that content and follow the procedures set forth in the Digital Millennium Copyright Act, 17 U.S.C. ยง 512(g). You can read more about that process at our ",
