													"value": "In addition to the information we provide as part of our abuse reporting process, Cloudflare also offers additional resources to help rightsholders investigating possible infringement. We provide information in response to valid subpoenas issued under the Digital Millennium Copyright Act, 17 U.S.C. ยง 512(h). We also have extended our trusted reporter program to certain rightsholder organizations to allow them to get access to sensitive origin IP address information we cannot otherwise make available due to security concerns. More generally, we regularly communicate with such organizations, relevant government entities, and with law enforcement to make sure we identify the best ways that we can help assist rightsholders consistent with the nature of the services that we provide.",
